name: Money Hoes & Clothes
description:
This tshirt is inspired by one of my favourite rappers of all time, the Notorious B.I.G. Here, I visualise the lyrics of Money Hoes and Clothes, with detail of the Coogi Sweater he was famously photographed in. 

These Regular fit White Fruit of Loom tshirts have my original hip hop inspired designs screen printed onto them. I print them myself at home, with a lot of effort, care and time spent on perfecting each garment. 

I hope you enjoy wearing your tshirt, as much as I enjoy making them!


These tshirts are customisable, with the option of being tie dyed 1 or two colours or your choice. Have a look at the "Customisation" page in the sidebar for more details. Feel free to message me with any queries or requests.

The tie dying is part of a custom service that I offer. Whilst I ensure my skill and passion has gone into these shirts, the results of tie dying are variable.
